{
  "texts": [
    "Instead, when considering what eye tracker to chose, we advise readers to:",
    "Let the research context and questions guide the choice of eye tracker. 2.",
    "Evaluate the eye tracker and test whether it is suitable to conduct the intended research. 3.",
    "Consider the whole eye-tracker setup, and not only the eye tracker. 4.",
    "Discuss the choice of eye tracker with researchers who are working in similar fields."
  ]
}